cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for clinical text classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses deep learning methods, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper uses convolutional neural networks, which could also suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
